<p>I won a prize for <a href="http://ohlordy.theapproachablegeek.co.uk/">Oh Lordy!</a> too, which was nice, and whilst presenting  UK Unemployment API found out that the thing I had built already exists in the form of <a href="http://www.nomisweb.co.uk/api/v01">NOMIS‚Äôs API</a>, and bloody good it is too.  Oh Lordy! also <a href="https://twitter.com/#!/jimpknight/status/133120837506170880">got tweeted about by Lord Knight</a> too, which was pretty cool.</p>
