 <p>A quick and dirty bit of data analysis using my tool or choice, Excel (and more specifically pivot tables).  This is a really rough cut and I‚Äôll be running the data through Google Refine (which I‚Äôve just been introduced to), but here‚Äôs the first cut of How Rude Are Countries.  It‚Äôs taken from 2010 Edinburgh Festival Fringe performance data provided via festivalslab and collates the Adult Content Warnings against the country of origin.</p>

