"_I‚Äôm Oli Wood (and as I write this, I‚Äôm 31) and I run The Approachable Geek.  I‚Äôm keenly involved in the North East tech scene, and in the last year have spoken at [Super Mondays](http://www.supermondays.org/) events and helped curate and compare Design It Build It [2010](http://lanyrd.com/2010/dibi/) and [2011](http://lanyrd.com/2011/dibi/) and then ran all of [2012](http://lanyrd.com/2012/dibi/).

